chat_history.content:
As of my knowledge cutoff date of January 2023, the last five presidents of the People's Republic of China were Xi Jinping, Hu Jintao, Jiang Zemin, Yang Shangkun, and Li Xiannian. 

The current president, Xi Jinping, was born in Beijing. 

Hu Jintao, his predecessor, was born in Taizhou, Jiangsu. 

Jiang Zemin was born in the city of Yangzhou, Jiangsu. 

Yang Shangkun's birthplace is not listed in the sources I have access to. 

Li Xiannian, the second president of the PRC, was born in Huangpi, Hubei.
